# Python cache & bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environment
venv/

# Environment variables
.env

# VS Code settings
.vscode/

# MacOS
.DS_Store

# Pytest / coverage
htmlcov/
.coverage
.pytest_cache/

# Node / Frontend
node_modules/
dist/
frontend/dist/

# Build artifacts
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# Logs
*.log
```

Key additions:
```
.pytest_cache/    → test runner cache (Sprint 11)
node_modules/     → frontend dependencies (never push these)
dist/             → frontend build output
*.log             → any log files generated at runtime